orax (2012) and 21 Jump Street (2012). After graduating from the University of Kansas with a B.A. in Theater and Film, Riggle joined the Marines and earned a Master\'s degree from Webster University in Public Administration. A featured cast member onSaturday Night Live (1975) during the 2004/2005 season, Riggle then joined Comedy Central\'s The Daily Show (1996) in 2006 as a correspondent. Riggle\'s numerous television appearances, including credits on Chappelle\'s Show (2003), 30 Rock (2006) and The Office (2005) would lead to big-screen roles in FVery Bad Trip (2009) and Very Bad Cops (2010). When he is not on set or traveling across the United States performing stand-up comedy, Rob Riggle lives in Los Angeles.','1970-04-21',NULL),(2543,'Marianne M. Arreaga','San Francisco, California, USA','Marianne M. Arreaga is an actress and stuntwoman.',NULL,NULL),(2544,'Taylor Sheridan','Cranfills Gap, Texas, USA','Taylor Sheridan (born May 21, 1970) is an American actor, screenwriter and director. He is most known for his role as David Hale on the FX television series Sons of Anarchy, and for writing the screenplay of the Denis Villeneuve-directed Sicario (2015), for which he received a Writers Guild of America Award nomination for Best Original Screenplay.\n\nHe also wrote the screenplay for Hell or High Water (2016), starring Jeff Bridges, Chris Pine and Ben Foster, which was released in August 2016 and earned Sheridan an Academy Award nomination for Best Original Screenplay. Wind River, starring Jeremy Renner and Elizabeth Olsen and the script for which he also penned, was released in August 2017. He is the brother of journalist John Gibler.','1970-05-21',NULL),(2545,'Kenda Henthorn',NULL,'',NULL,NULL),(2546,'Gary Glushon',NULL,'',NULL,NULL),(2547,'Jade Chynoweth','Park City, Utah, USA','Jade Chynoweth is an American actress and dancer. She is known for her roles as young Artemisia in the 2014 epic historical fantasy war film 300: Rise of an Empire and Carmen in the 2016